<activity xml:id="act-faltaInfo-competenciaDePesosDeCalabazas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Problem Card 1: 65 kg. Sample response: Since the pumpkin’s weight increased 13 kilograms each day for 5 days, I multiplied <m>5 \times 13 = 65</m>.</p>
<p>Problem Card 2: 12 kilograms each day. Sample response: I knew the pumpkin’s weight increased 72 kilograms over 6 days and had gained the same amount each day, so I divided <m>72 \div 6 = 12</m>.</p>
  </solution>


